CONTACT: Lovci na oluje Dubrovnik (Storm chasers Dubrovnik) (VON)
EVENT_DESCRIPTION: Heavy rain with peak intensity of 288 mm/h (19:34UTC) in the area of Dubrovnik. The amount 87 mm  was measured by Storm Chasers Dubrovnik automatic weather station (Davis Vue 6250) located on the elementary school Mokosica. Most of the rain fell between 18:00 UTC and 20:30 UTC.    The official report by Croatian Meteorological and Hydrological Service was 69.9 mm, measured at Gorica (~3.8 km SW from Mokosica).  The rain was followed by thunder.
REFERENCE: Obilna kiša u Dubrovniku pogledajte kako izgleda vožnja gradom, Index.hr, 29 Jan 2021.
